videos.description: Auburn's Chuma Okeke saves the ball from going out of bounds which leads to the Horace Spencer dunk at the other end.
videos.headline: Spencer gets slam dunk off saved rebound

videos.description: Auburn's Samir Doughty gets the ball on the fastbreak and Eurosteps his way to a layup to end the half on a 8-0 run.
videos.headline: Doughty hits the Eurostep for layup
